        "subject": "LU-8969 utils: avoid use of O_DIRECT in lfs_migrate",
        "message": "LU-8969 utils: avoid use of O_DIRECT in lfs_migrate\n\nPrecise failure behavior on O_DIRECT reads at file EOF differs\non newer linux versions.\nStop using O_DIRECT to avoid the problem entirely.\n\nSigned-off-by: Bob Glossman <bob.glossman@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Id909a72639aa71418801d6913efac96a9556f5b6\n"
      },
